description: Filter out duplicates in an array
readme:
## uniques

Filter out duplicates in an array

## Install

```bash
$ npm install uniques
```

## Usage

```js
uniques([3, 1, 4, 1, 5, 6, 6, 5, 2])
// => [3, 1, 4, 5, 6, 2]
```
